text: Novoishmetovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Staroyantuzovsky Selsoviet,Dyurtyulinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 79 as of 2010. There are 4 streets. == Geography == It is located 25 km from Dyurtyuli. == References == Category:Rural localities in Dyurtyulinsky District
title: Novoishmetovo
